Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.40,0:00:03.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,《指定幸存者》前情提要\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Previously on "Designated Survivor"...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.45,0:00:04.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关于北约峰会\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's about the NATO summit.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.45,0:00:07.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新任法国大使想谈谈核弹的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The new French ambassador wanted to talk about nukes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.15,0:00:08.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们愿意逐步削减军备\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's an opening to De-escalate.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.75,0:00:11.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里的炸药足够炸毁三座国会大厦了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There's enough explosives in here to blow up three Capitols.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.00,0:00:13.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她被绑架了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She's been kidnapped.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.08,0:00:14.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她在查布朗宁·里德\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She was looking into Browning Reed.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.85,0:00:16.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,威尔士探员认为其前任执行董事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Agent Wells is convinced that
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.00,0:00:18.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帕特里克·劳埃德涉嫌参与这起阴谋\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the ex-C.E.O. Patrick Lloyd's involved with the conspiracy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.46,0:00:20.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会清除你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm brooming any connection between you,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.31,0:00:22.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布朗宁·里德以及国会任务之间的联系\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Browning Reed, and the Capitol mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.03,0:00:24.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很快  就不会再有书面记录等等的问题\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Soon, there'll be no paper trail whatsoever,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.12,0:00:25.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且威尔士探员已被抓获\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and Agent Wells is contained.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.03,0:00:27.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,埃布·莱纳德已经消化了我给他的一切\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Abe Leonard has eaten up everything I've fed him.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.82,0:00:29.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我们什么时候能看到他采取行动\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When are we gonna see something from him, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.11,0:00:30.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该快了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Any day, I expect.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.50,0:00:34.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自从国会袭击案之后\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Since the attack at the Capitol,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.90,0:00:37.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,提及到布朗宁·里德的文件都被删除了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}references to Browning Reed have been deleted.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.00,0:00:38.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我们找到删除文件的人...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If we find out who deleted these files...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.99,0:00:40.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们就找到了叛徒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}we find our traitor.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.57,0:00:54.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,注意  所有安保队...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Be advised. All security teams...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.52,0:02:12.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赛斯  你还好吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey, Seth, you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.71,0:02:17.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没事  抱歉  我不知道是怎么了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, I'm sorry. Uh, I-I don't know what's happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.87,0:02:19.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我通常不会晕机的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I-I don't usually get airsick.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.13,0:02:22.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想想的话  这也是你第一次坐空军一号\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And to think, it's your first time on Air Force One, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.39,0:02:25.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赛斯  看着\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey, Seth, look.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.34,0:02:28.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可以把这张照片也发给你妈\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You can send this one to your mom, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.29,0:02:31.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该打起精神了  孩子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Time to rally, son.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.57,0:02:34.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们着陆前得先应对媒体\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We got to gaggle with the press before we land.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.88,0:02:46.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请进\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.22,0:02:49.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在不方便吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Bad time?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.35,0:02:51.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会  请进\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No. Come on in.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.35,0:02:53.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I, uh --
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.79,0:02:56.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得第一次参加国际峰会的压力\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I think the pressure of his first international summit
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.18,0:02:58.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能把你的新闻发言人吓住了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}may have gotten to your press secretary.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.82,0:03:00.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道你感觉怎么样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I just wondered how you're doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.54,0:03:02.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很好  赛斯没事吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm fine. Is Seth all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.12,0:03:04.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他没事  只是有点紧张\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, just a case of the jitters.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.02,0:03:06.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他会没事的  只要他明白\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He'll get over it as soon as he realizes
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.84,0:03:08.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,北约峰会无非就是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that a NATO summit is no different
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.53,0:03:11.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多语种的超大型内阁会议而已\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}than an outsized cabinet meeting in a lot of different languages.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.54,0:03:14.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望能有那么简单\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I hope it's that simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.13,0:03:17.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是我直接提出方案\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Are they gonna think that it's presumptuous of me,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.19,0:03:18.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们会觉得我太专横了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}putting an initiative on the table?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.70,0:03:22.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然不会  你可是美国总统\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hell no. You're the president of the United States.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.86,0:03:23.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也对\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.50,0:03:26.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道我并非像你那般的谈判者\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know I'm not the negotiator that you are --
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.59,0:03:28.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别看轻自己\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ah, don't sell yourself short.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.35,0:03:30.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,汤姆  也许我们的处事风格不同\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You know, we may have different styles, Tom,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.82,0:03:32.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但这恰恰是一个好团队所必须的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but I think that's what makes us a good team.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.41,0:03:35.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有学者也有政客\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The professor and the politician.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.32,0:03:38.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你负责提供事实  我负责强迫他们接受\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You give them the facts, and I'll twist their arms.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.68,0:03:39.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That works for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.93,0:03:43.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道这对你来说有多重要\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know how important this is to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.09,0:03:46.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.80,0:03:50.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果当初我连任  军备控制本会是我的首要目标\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The arms control was going to be a priority of my second term.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.39,0:03:54.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在这是我们的首要目标\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well... now it's our priority.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.09,0:03:59.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不关心你们加了多少班\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't care about your overtime.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.33,0:04:01.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  你们得找遍每个角落\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, you search everywhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.47,0:04:03.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是都找过了  就再找一遍\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and then when you've done that, search it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.45,0:04:06.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是没发现吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Still nothing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.44,0:04:08.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有  我让国内的所有机构都去找了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No. I got every agency in the country looking.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.09,0:04:11.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她知道怎么照顾自己\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She knows how to take care of herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.83,0:04:12.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.34,0:04:15.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布朗宁·里德查得怎么样了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where are you with the Browning Reed investigation?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.15,0:04:16.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我让恰克·拉辛克来帮忙了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I got Chuck Russink coming in to help out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.88,0:04:19.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拉辛克  不是吧  他可不靠谱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Russink? You serious? He's a space cadet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.35,0:04:21.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,汉娜相信他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hannah trusts him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.47,0:04:23.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来真是不顾一切了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Whatever it takes, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.87,0:04:26.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我准备买单的  罗迪斯女士\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I was gonna pay, Ms. Rhodes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.38,0:04:27.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的不用  我来就行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, seriously. I'll get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.61,0:04:29.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,服务员呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where's our server?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.26,0:04:36.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失陪一下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Will you guys excuse me a second?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.50,0:04:37.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.15,0:04:43.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey, you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.54,0:04:46.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好  很高兴见到你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How you doing? It's good to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.14,0:04:48.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾米丽·罗迪斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Emily Rhodes,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.91,0:04:50.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我表妹纳迪娅·埃斯皮诺萨\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}meet my cousin, Nadia Espinosa.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.36,0:04:52.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很高兴见到你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's a pleasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.77,0:04:55.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你老板是吉田议员  对吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You work for Congresswoman Yoshida, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.88,0:04:56.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.70,0:04:58.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-怎么样  -我很喜欢这工作\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- How's that going? - I love it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.14,0:05:02.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很高兴能跟优秀的人一起合作\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I mean, it's great to be able to collaborate with good people.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.75,0:05:04.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们俩真的是亲戚吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Are you sure you two are related?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.35,0:05:06.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  我也觉得奇怪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, I wonder all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.47,0:05:11.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想再来一杯啤酒  你们需要什么吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I need another beer. Do you guys want anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.39,0:05:12.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-不用了  谢谢  -不用了  谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- No, I'm good, thanks. - No, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.80,0:05:16.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说总统去多伦多了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So, POTUS is heading up to Toronto.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.46,0:05:18.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  白宫归我管了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes. The White House is all mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.00,0:05:20.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说正经的  这是他第一次参加北约峰会\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, seriously, it's his first NATO summit.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.86,0:05:22.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一次作为总统出国\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}First time out of the country.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.36,0:05:23.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,民调支持率很高\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Polls are high.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.89,0:05:25.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他势如破竹  你也是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I mean, he's on a roll. So are you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.72,0:05:27.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不得不承认  这感觉很爽\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I do have to admit, it feels good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.27,0:05:30.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你呢  你会继续跟着霍斯拉滕吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What about you? Are you gonna follow Hookstraten?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.76,0:05:32.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  她是邀请我了  不过\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, she did offer, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.86,0:05:35.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得我不适合为教育部长工作\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't see myself working for the Secretary of Education.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.77,0:05:37.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这工作可不刺激\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's not exactly the fast lane.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.47,0:05:39.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么说吧  在白宫工作过后\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let's just say, after you work in the West Wing,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.29,0:05:41.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其他任何工作都感觉是被贬了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}everything feels like a step down.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.13,0:05:43.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可要知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, just so you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.28,0:05:45.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我并没有反对让霍斯拉滕当副总统\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I was not opposed to Hookstraten for V.P.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.77,0:05:48.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得要是能继续合作就更好了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I think it would've been great to be working together again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.20,0:05:49.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  一定的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, it would've been.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.38,0:05:51.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是华盛顿  什么都有可能发生  对吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's Washington. Anything can happen, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.25,0:05:53.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通常是的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And it usually does.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.72,0:05:55.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.13,0:05:58.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我该回去了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I should get back.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.55,0:05:59.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢过来打招呼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thanks for stopping by.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.62,0:06:16.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们会参加一个半小时的接待会\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So, we attend the general reception for 30 minutes,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.24,0:06:17.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,照照相什么的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}smile for the cameras,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.74,0:06:19.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后我们就回迎宾套房\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}then we retreat to a hospitality suite
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.89,0:06:21.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是我为与北约核计划小组几个\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I set up for select members
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.98,0:06:23.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特定成员国的领导人会面而准备的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}of the Nuclear Planning Group.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.09,0:06:26.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样我们就能在全体大会前\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That gives us a chance to start some lobbying
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.26,0:06:28.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-进行游说了  -这招厉害\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- before the general session. - Smart.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.32,0:06:30.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是老手了  年轻人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, it's not my first rodeo, son.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.11,0:06:32.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的首要目标\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now, our primary target
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.26,0:06:36.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是法国总理贾丝廷·马塞特\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}is French Prime Minister Justine Massett.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.45,0:06:39.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷厉风行  且如圣女贞德般爱国\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sharp as a tack and as chauvinistic as Joan of Arc.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.45,0:06:39.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}法国传奇女英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.64,0:06:42.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她可能会很难对付\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She can be very prickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.57,0:06:44.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么呢  一开始可是法国想要\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why would she be? It was the French who wanted us
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.39,0:06:46.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我们提出裁减军备的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to bring up arms reduction in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.18,0:06:48.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但那是私下说的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes. Privately.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.60,0:06:51.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但在北约其他国家面前\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But in front of NATO,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.05,0:06:53.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,法国想让我们先提出这个议案\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the French want us to bring up the initiative first,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.74,0:06:56.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好让他们有个机会先批评一下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}giving them an opportunity to criticize
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.46,0:06:58.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果他们想的话  甚至可以食言\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}or even withdraw, if they so choose.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.02,0:07:00.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这都是套路\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's all part of the game --
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.55,0:07:02.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没到必要的时候别当出头鸟\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}don't stick your neck out if you don't have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.47,0:07:05.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下一个是乔纳斯·格洛特克\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Then there's Jonas Grottke,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.03,0:07:08.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚刚连任德国总理\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}just re-elected as German Chancellor.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.57,0:07:11.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同时他也是北约核计划小组的主席\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's also a chairman of NATO's Nuclear Planning Group.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.61,0:07:13.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,强大的盟友  他能为你说话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Strong ally. Got you covered there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.79,0:07:15.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好  需要担心的事情又少了点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Good. One less thing for me to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.90,0:07:18.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而我不了解的人是阿鲁娜·马哈詹\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The one unknown to me is Aruna Mahajan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.42,0:07:22.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,英国史上第一位印度裔首相\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The first British Indian prime minister in U.K. history.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.00,0:07:26.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,极端的无党派者  但能在极其动荡的情况下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Fiercely independent but was able to forge a coalition
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.33,0:07:30.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,建立起政治联盟\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and under extremely turbulent conditions.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.30,0:07:31.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们有一些共同点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, we have something in common.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.37,0:07:33.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确实\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}True enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.32,0:07:34.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I can work with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.16,0:07:37.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.74,0:07:38.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.96,0:08:18.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求救  求救  我是联调局探员\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mayday, mayday. This is FBI Agent
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.02,0:08:19.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,汉娜·威尔士  求救\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hannah Wells. Mayday.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.81,0:08:21.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,联调局探员汉娜·威尔士  求救\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}FBI Agent Hannah Wells. Mayday.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.39,0:08:24.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求救  我是...汉娜·威尔士\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mayday. This is... Hannah Wells.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.53,0:08:29.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,汉娜·威尔士  这里是印第安河流域\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hannah Wells, this is Coast Guard Station 142,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.03,0:08:30.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海岸警卫队142号站\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Indian River.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.47,0:08:36.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海岸警卫队142号站呼叫汉娜·威尔士船只\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Coast Guard Station 142 calling the ship Hannah Wells.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.08,0:08:40.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是联调局探员汉娜·威尔士\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is FBI Agent Hannah Wells.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.52,0:08:41.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mayda...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.17,0:09:13.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先  我要感谢各位的出席\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}To begin, I want to thank you all for being here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.97,0:09:17.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正如你们知道的  明天除了常规安排以外\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}As you know, in addition to tomorrow's regular schedule,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.56,0:09:19.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美国将会提出一个缩减\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the United States will be introducing an initiative
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.98,0:09:22.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,北约成员国核武库的提案\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that would reduce NATO's nuclear arsenal.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.47,0:09:23.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想要明确一点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now, I want to be absolutely clear
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.99,0:09:26.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是一项削减军备的提案\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that this is a proposed weapons-reduction change,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.25,0:09:27.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并非正式声明\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}not a change in doctrine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.51,0:09:31.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且这完全建立在俄罗斯联邦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And it's entirely predicated upon the Russian Federation
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.20,0:09:34.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,响应北约号召\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}scaling back its strategic nuclear weapons
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.20,0:09:37.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而按比缩减战略性核武器的基础上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}in proportional response to NATO's actions,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.45,0:09:39.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,俄罗斯总统已向我保证\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}something that the Russian president
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.03,0:09:41.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他已经准备好实施了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}has assured me he is ready to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.71,0:09:43.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你相信他吗  科内留斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What, you believe him, Cornelius?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.56,0:09:44.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  我相信\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.09,0:09:45.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,基于什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}On what basis?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.86,0:09:48.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,基于我们二十年的情谊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}On the basis of our 20-year relationship
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.81,0:09:51.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能准确分辨出他是否在撒谎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and being able to tell when he's lying and when he's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.31,0:09:57.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且还建立在能使我们的家园变得\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And based on the fact that it is in the interest of all sides
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.48,0:09:58.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更稳定  更安全的举措\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to agree on anything
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.23,0:10:01.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是完全符合各国利益的事实基础之上的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that will lead to a more stable and secure planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.06,0:10:05.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尽管最近世界秩序遭到破坏\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Despite recent disruptions to the world order,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.31,0:10:09.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但现在不是回去搞孤立主义或民粹主义的时候\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}this is not the time to retreat into isolationism or populism.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.50,0:10:12.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在是展现全球合作可以也将会\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is the time to show that global cooperation
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.69,0:10:14.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,指引我们创造更安全的未来的时候\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}can and will lead us to a safer future.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.78,0:10:18.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更何况我们用以保管核武器的设备方法\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not to mention that the way that we keep our nuclear arsenals
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.12,0:10:20.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,耗资巨大\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}is insanely expensive.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.41,0:10:23.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真有趣  总统先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's intriguing, Mr. President,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.49,0:10:26.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但波兰和斯洛伐克没有核武器\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but Poland and Slovakia have no nuclear weapons of our own.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.85,0:10:29.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们依赖美国提供的"核保护伞"\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We rely on your American nuclear umbrellas.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.68,0:10:33.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你要如何保证削减核军备后\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So what can you offer by way of a guarantee
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.42,0:10:37.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的和平与安全依然能受到保护呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that our peace and our safety will still be protected?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.25,0:10:43.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在我能给的只是承诺\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The closest thing I can offer to a guarantee is my word,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.98,0:10:45.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是以汤姆·柯克曼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}not as Tom Kirkman,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.52,0:10:47.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是以美国总统的身份作出的承诺\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but as President of the United States,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.72,0:10:49.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你最坚定的盟友\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}your most steadfast ally.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.88,0:10:51.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可以相信他  约瑟夫\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You can believe him there, Jozef.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.33,0:10:53.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们都能相信他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We can all believe him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.27,0:10:57.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很显然  我希望明天峰会能获得你们的支持\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Obviously, I am hoping for your support at tomorrow's summit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.67,0:10:58.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.84,0:11:01.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,法方很期待你的提案\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}France looks forward to your proposal.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.95,0:11:03.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感激不尽  女士\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I appreciate that, Madame.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.27,0:11:12.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是白宫之旅\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This isn't on the White House tour.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.14,0:11:16.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,进出威尔士探员办公室的通道是受到严格保密的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Access to Agent Wells' office is extremely restricted.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.91,0:11:17.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,汉娜在哪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where is Hannah?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.30,0:11:20.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出外勤了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}On assignment.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.58,0:11:28.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能恢复那些被删的关于布朗宁·里德的文件吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Any chance we can recover those deleted Browning Reed files?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.41,0:11:29.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是说不用时光机吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not without a time machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.33,0:11:32.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人运行了一个强制删除程序\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Someone ran a brute-force deletion program.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.67,0:11:34.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是数据清除工具的始祖\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's the mother of data erasers.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.41,0:11:36.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经把数据从白宫服务器上彻底删除了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Cleaned them right off the White House servers.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.58,0:11:37.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我们什么都查不到了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So we got nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.96,0:11:39.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可没这么说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I didn't say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.60,0:11:41.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为一开始有大批文件需要处理\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Because there were so many files to begin with,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.18,0:11:42.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管是谁在湮灭证据\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}whoever's been covering their tracks
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.59,0:11:45.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他在过去几个月里分多次少量删除了这批文件\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}has been deleting them in small batches over the past few months.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.79,0:11:47.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与布朗宁·里德有关的文件\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There are only five files
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.04,0:11:49.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在只剩下五份\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}still remaining associated with Browning Reed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.57,0:11:51.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你需要把它们拷贝并打印出来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Gonna need you to make copies and print them up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.31,0:11:53.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看一下这个\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Check this out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.15,0:11:56.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是删除档案的那个人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's a digital fingerprint left behind
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.54,0:11:58.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,留下的数位指纹\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}by the person who deleted the files.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.49,0:12:00.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,数位指纹是独一无二的  如果我够厉害\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now, they tend to be unique, but if I'm good --
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.81,0:12:02.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得自己的确挺厉害的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and I like to think I am --
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.16,0:12:05.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以在这些文件里植入追踪程序\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I can program a trace and plant it in the remaining files.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.72,0:12:07.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果叛徒试图删除其中任何一份文件\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So if the traitor tries to delete any of them,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.76,0:12:10.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们就能追踪到对方的IP地址\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}we can track the user back to an exact I.P. address.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.58,0:12:11.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正是如此\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.01,0:12:13.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你需要多长时间编写追踪程序\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How long will it take you to build a trace?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.58,0:12:16.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-几个小时吧  -给你一小时\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- A few hours? - You got one.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.62,0:12:19.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些文件是查出内鬼的唯一线索\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Those files are the only lead to the insider,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.09,0:12:21.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一旦被删除  就什么都不剩了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and once they're deleted, we got nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.89,0:12:22.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是"毫无压力"啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No pressure, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.03,0:12:34.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢  好的  非常感谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, thank you. Yes. Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.55,0:12:36.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搞定了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.15,0:12:38.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的提案被确定为第三项议程\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Our proposal is the third item on the agenda.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.06,0:12:40.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,胜利在望了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're on our way.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.05,0:12:41.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-现场没有媒体吧  -没有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- No media, right? - Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.34,0:12:45.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有你和其他27位国家领导人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just you and 27 other leaders of the free world.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.26,0:12:47.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放松点  汤姆\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Relax, Tom.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.48,0:12:51.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们想要的只是开启一个早就该进行的会谈\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All we're asking is to start a conversation that's long overdue.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.21,0:12:53.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请进\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.82,0:12:54.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赛斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Seth.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.60,0:12:57.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉打扰您  总统先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey. Sorry to disturb you, Mr. President.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.14,0:12:59.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是觉得您应该马上看看这个\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I just, um, thought you should see this right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.27,0:13:04.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}艾尔萨卡并非国会爆炸案的真凶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.16,0:13:10.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-为什么事先没人提醒我们  -有啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Why didn't we get a heads-up? - We did.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.10,0:13:12.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,几天前埃布问过我艾尔萨卡的事  记得吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Abe asked me about Al-Sakar a couple days ago, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.22,0:13:14.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.29,0:13:16.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们搪塞过去了  我以为这事已经了结了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We stonewalled. I thought that was the end of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.29,0:13:17.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但他还是发表了文章\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Then he published anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.98,0:13:19.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们接下来怎么办\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So, what's our plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.90,0:13:21.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这简直是胡说八道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is total crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.44,0:13:22.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们马上商量解决办法\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're figuring that out right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.74,0:13:23.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回头再打给你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll call you back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.38,0:13:26.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我认识埃布·莱纳德  他曾是位优秀的记者\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I knew Abe Leonard. He was a good reporter
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.26,0:13:29.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直到他开始利用消息来源肆意妄为\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}until he started getting fast and loose with his sources.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.57,0:13:31.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把这个新闻压下来对你来说应该不在话下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You should have no problem shooting this one down.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.54,0:13:33.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉他们这只是一派胡言\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just tell them it's nothing but a big pack of lies.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.08,0:13:36.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  我希望我们承认这是一种猜想\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, I want our position to be that this is conjecture,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.88,0:13:40.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我们会对所有的指控展开调查\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but we will investigate all of the allegations.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.20,0:13:41.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  总统先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sorry, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.20,0:13:42.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果这并非事实为何不直接公开否认呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why not just openly deny it if it's not true?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.92,0:13:43.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赛斯说得对\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Seth's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.90,0:13:46.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,此刻回避只会招来更多质疑声\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Deflecting this now is only gonna raise suspicion.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.77,0:13:48.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  美国公民相信我们抓获的恐怖分子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, the American people believe that we captured
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.77,0:13:50.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是国会爆炸案的真凶\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the terrorists responsible for the Capitol bombing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.71,0:13:53.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这篇报道扬言我们抓错了人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This article says that we got the wrong guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.49,0:13:55.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是说  如果我们现在不用力反击\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I mean, if we don't push back hard now,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.07,0:13:57.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,民众会对政府丧失信心的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}confidence in the administration's gonna tank.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.63,0:14:01.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可以说政府相信\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You can say that we're standing by
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.84,0:14:04.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的情报机构和军方官员\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}our intelligence agencies and our military officials.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.65,0:14:05.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  总统先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm sorry, Mr. President.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.61,0:14:06.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想这么做远远不够\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't think that goes far enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.52,0:14:08.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这么写  然后拿给我看\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just write it up and bring it back to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.89,0:14:09.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的  总统先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.93,0:14:19.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是怎么一回事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What the hell was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.24,0:14:21.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是我的处理方式\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's how I have to handle this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.07,0:14:27.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要知道这篇报道极大的损害了你的公信力\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You realize this story puts your credibility at risk.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.43,0:14:31.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果现在不粉碎谣言的话  你的就任百天计划\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Your 100 days, everything we want to do here,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.10,0:14:34.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们现在做的一切  全都会付之东流\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}goes right out the window if you don't crush this right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.15,0:14:36.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我无法这么做  -为什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I can't. - Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.15,0:14:39.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为这是真的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Because it's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.74,0:14:52.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难以置信\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Unbelievable.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.96,0:14:55.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本土阴谋\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A homegrown conspiracy?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.11,0:14:57.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白宫内的潜在叛徒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A possible traitor in the White House?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.61,0:14:58.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.41,0:15:00.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你都没告诉我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And you didn't tell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.10,0:15:02.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事关国家安全\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It was a matter of security.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.15,0:15:04.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾米丽和赛斯都不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Emily doesn't know. Neither does Seth.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.04,0:15:06.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是你的国务卿啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, I'm your Secretary of State, for God's sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.10,0:15:08.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是在总统继承顺位上啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I mean, I-I'm in the line of succession.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.13,0:15:09.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉得你无法信任我吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You didn't think you could trust me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.24,0:15:11.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-这和信任无关  -胡说八道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- This isn't a matter of trust. - The hell it's not!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.12,0:15:13.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了你我重新出山\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now, I came out of retirement for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.40,0:15:15.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我把我的一世英名交到你的手上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I put my legacy on the line for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.13,0:15:15.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就是这样报答我的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And this is how you repay me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.88,0:15:18.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我以为我控制住局面了  -你错了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I thought I had it handled. - Well, you were wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.39,0:15:19.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你大错特错\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You were dead wrong,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.07,0:15:20.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在我和你成了一根线上的蚂蚱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and now my head is on the block right along with yours!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.93,0:15:22.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我应该早点让你知道的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, I probably should've let you in.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.42,0:15:24.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这真是年度最不负责任的陈述啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That is the understatement of the year.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.64,0:15:26.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我见过你之前的判断失误\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I have seen you exercise poor judgment before,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.74,0:15:27.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但都无法和这次相比  汤姆\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tom, but this takes the cake!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.84,0:15:29.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,科内留斯  如果我冒犯你了我很抱歉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Cornelius, I'm sorry if I offended you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.59,0:15:31.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不想这样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's the last thing I wanted to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.15,0:15:33.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是美国总统有义务\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But the president of the United States has a responsibility
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.53,0:15:37.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保护机密信息和正在进行的调查\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to protect classified information and ongoing investigations.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.62,0:15:40.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这根本不是意图误导美国民众\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This isn't a matter of trying to mislead the American people.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.21,0:15:42.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是为了保护他们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is about trying to protect them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.19,0:15:43.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你应该了解这点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And you should know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.75,0:15:47.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我犯了错  我很抱歉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now, I've made a mistake, and I am sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.08,0:15:51.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但现在我需要你的指导\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But right now I need your counsel.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.47,0:15:52.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有哪些选择\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What are my options?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.47,0:15:58.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,问题是你没有任何选择\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You don't have any. That's the problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.48,0:16:01.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不作伪证的话无法否认这篇报道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You can't deny the story without committing perjury,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.90,0:16:03.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不承认你仍不知道真凶身份的话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and you can't confirm it without admitting
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.68,0:16:05.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就无法证实这篇报道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that you still don't know who's behind all this,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.60,0:16:08.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这会让整个美国陷入恐慌\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}throwing the whole American country into a panic.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.14,0:16:10.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我们需要赛斯帮我们争取些时间\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's why we need Seth to buy us some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.47,0:16:11.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,需要多久\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But how much time?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.86,0:16:13.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总统先生  我们已经身处狼穴了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The jackals are at the door, Mr. President.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.86,0:16:16.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得我们快知道真相了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I think we're really close to cracking this thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.23,0:16:17.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do you really?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.75,0:16:20.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的首席探员失踪了  可能已经死了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Your lead investigator is missing, possibly dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.41,0:16:22.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,试图杀你的人依旧活着\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The man who tried to kill you is still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.43,0:16:25.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白宫里的叛徒身份依然成谜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And the mole in the White House remains unknown.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.64,0:16:28.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我看来你就好像全押在了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It looks to me like you're doubling down
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.25,0:16:29.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一手特别烂的牌上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}on a mighty poor hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.76,0:16:31.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我别无选择了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, it's the only hand I was given.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.81,0:16:35.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.66,0:16:38.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们只有厚着脸皮上了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We brass it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.44,0:16:46.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是摩斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is Moss.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.96,0:16:48.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.52,0:16:51.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然  我们马上就到\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Of course. We'll be right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.72,0:16:56.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的盟友希望我们到楼下去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Our allies have requested our presence downstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.00,0:17:01.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们希望我们能解释一下那篇报道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They want an explanation for the story.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.80,0:17:07.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎回来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.62,0:17:08.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们邀请到\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're joined now
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.32,0:17:10.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天《纽约标准》报道的作者\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}by Pulitzer Prize-winning journalist Abe Leonard,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.01,0:17:12.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,普利策奖得主埃布·莱纳德\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}whose story in today's New York Standard
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.64,0:17:14.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该报道挑起了一系列严峻的问题\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}has raised serious questions
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.94,0:17:26.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}艾尔萨卡并非国会爆炸案的真凶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.37,0:17:18.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底谁才是国会爆炸案的真凶\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}about who was really responsible for the attack on our Capitol.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.07,0:17:20.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-欢迎你  埃布  -谢谢  很高兴来到这里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Welcome, Abe. - Thank you. It's good to be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.18,0:17:21.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们由头条标题说起吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let's start with the big headline.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.29,0:17:24.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾尔萨卡没有炸毁国会大厦吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Al-Sakar did not blow up the Capitol?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.09,0:17:27.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有  他们没有相应的人力财力\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No. They didn't have the money or the manpower.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.08,0:17:30.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们的头目马吉德·纳萨尔是为了钱出来背锅的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Their leader, Majid Nassar, was paid to take credit.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.79,0:17:32.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁给的钱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Paid? By whom?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.02,0:17:34.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,内斯特·洛萨诺\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nestor Lozano,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.23,0:17:36.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,试图行刺柯克曼总统的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the man who tried to assassinate President Kirkman.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.93,0:17:38.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但政府却将目标锁定在马吉德·纳萨尔身上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yet our government went after Majid Nassar --
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.95,0:17:40.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们在一次海豹突击行动中将纳萨尔抓获\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}actually captured him in a S.E.A.L. team raid
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.92,0:17:42.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突击队指挥官也在那次行动中殉职\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}where the commanding officer was killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.94,0:17:44.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我认为他们被误导了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I believe they were misled.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.94,0:17:46.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被谁误导了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Misled by whom?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.71,0:17:47.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差劲的情报机关\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Bad intelligence.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.98,0:17:50.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们相信了洛萨诺设的套\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They bought the story Lozano was selling.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.58,0:17:52.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那洛萨诺到底在保护谁呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But who was he protecting?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.83,0:17:53.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}静音
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.02,0:17:59.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是惠特克\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Whitaker.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.90,0:18:01.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有看埃布·莱纳德在电视上的讲话吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Are you watching Abe Leonard on television?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.40,0:18:04.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没  但我看了他的报道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, but I read his story.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.25,0:18:07.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奏效了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's all working.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.31,0:18:10.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有人的注意力都在联调局那边  而非我们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Everyone's focused on the FBI, not us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.76,0:18:14.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好  但他从哪里获得了洛萨诺的消息\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, that's great, but where did he get this stuff about Lozano?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.63,0:18:16.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道  是他自己做的调查\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't know. He did that on his own.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.63,0:18:18.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么他踩入了雷区\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, he's treading on dangerous ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.53,0:18:20.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不算吧  他认为洛萨诺死了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not really. He thinks Lozano's dead,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.12,0:18:21.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和其他人一样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}just like everyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.55,0:18:25.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}艾尔萨卡并非国会爆炸案的真凶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.52,0:18:28.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,埃布·莱纳德已经没有利用价值了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Abe Leonard has served his purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.67,0:18:30.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Roger that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.08,0:18:35.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正如我所说  总统非常相信\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}As I said, the president stands
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.50,0:18:38.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的情报机关以及军方机构\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}by our intelligence community and our military.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.14,0:18:38.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回答问题  赛斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Answer the question, Seth.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.95,0:18:40.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾尔萨卡炸毁了国会大厦吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Did Al-Sakar blow up the Capitol?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.43,0:18:42.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根据当前的官方说法  是艾尔萨卡没错\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That is the official explanation at this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.52,0:18:43.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有改变的可能性是吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But it could change?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.40,0:18:45.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只想说  我们正深入展开调查\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All I said is we're looking into the allegations.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.61,0:18:47.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这意味着  你并不清楚吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So does that mean you don't know?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.24,0:18:48.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是意味着调查正在进行中\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It means we're looking into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.60,0:18:50.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-赛斯  -请提问\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Seth! - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.84,0:18:52.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,柯克曼总统在北约峰会上讲的是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}El presidente Kirkman está  diciendo la verdad
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.74,0:18:53.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真话吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}a la cumbre De la OTAN?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.82,0:18:55.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听到了吗  终于有关于北约的问题了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ah, see? A question about NATO.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.34,0:18:56.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很遗憾  我的西班牙语不是很好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Unfortunately, my Spanish is no longer as good.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.89,0:18:57.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能重复一遍问题吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Could you repeat the question?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.88,0:18:58.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请谅解\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Perdon.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.64,0:19:01.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,柯克曼总统在北约峰会上讲的是实话吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is President Kirkman telling the NATO summit the truth?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.90,0:19:02.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经回答过这个问题了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've already answered this question.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.98,0:19:04.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然是实话啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Of course he's telling the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.61,0:19:07.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}《纽约标准》
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.95,0:19:07.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果总统相信他的情报机构\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If the president stands by his intelligence,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.81,0:19:09.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么还要对该指控展开调查呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}why is he looking into the allegations?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.91,0:19:11.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直在明确这点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sure. So, I've tried to be perfectly clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.79,0:19:14.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想要答案  总统也是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You want answers. The president wants answers.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.45,0:19:16.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以他才展开调查  知道吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Which is why he is looking into the allegations, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.94,0:19:19.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍后他会寻找一个恰当的时间\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And he'll make a statement to the public
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.04,0:19:19.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发表公开讲话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}at the appropriate time,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.74,0:19:24.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}白宫针对国会爆炸案模棱两可的回应
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.98,0:19:22.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但如今他正专注于他的首次北约峰会之行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but right now he is focused on the first NATO summit,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.80,0:19:24.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我想大家提一些关于这方面的问题\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}which is what I would love to answer questions about.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.10,0:19:34.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是法索\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is Foerstel.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.29,0:19:35.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特别探员法索\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Special Agent Foerstel,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.55,0:19:37.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是军士长露西·费尔南德兹\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}this is Chief Petty Officer Lucy Fernandez,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.79,0:19:40.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隶属海岸警卫队  负责特拉华州印第安河流域\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}U.S. Coast Guard, Indian River, Delaware.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.55,0:19:43.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们昨晚收到了汉娜·威尔士的求救信号\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We received a mayday call from Hannah Wells last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.05,0:19:46.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你们找到她了吗  -还没有  先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- You found her? - Not exactly, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.29,0:19:47.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由于求救信号受到了静电干扰\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Uh, because of the static of the distress call,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.62,0:19:49.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们起初以为汉娜·威尔士是一艘船\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}we thought that Hannah Wells was a ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.58,0:19:52.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,使用数字滤波器对信号进行处理后\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It wasn't until we ran the call through a digital filter
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.11,0:19:55.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们才意识到她说的是"联调局探员威尔士"\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that we realized she was saying "FBI Agent Hannah Wells."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.16,0:19:56.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没明白\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay. I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.85,0:19:59.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你到底找到她没有  -没有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Do you have her or not? - We don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.31,0:20:00.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了回应求救信号\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In response to the mayday,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.24,0:20:02.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们紧急出动了一艘H-65救援直升机及救生船\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}we scrambled an H-65 helicopter and a response boat
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.92,0:20:03.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前往信号发射地\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to the coordinates,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.50,0:20:04.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但一无所获\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but the results were negative.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.97,0:20:06.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧  所以现在是什么情况\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay. So where does this leave us?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.64,0:20:07.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们正扩大搜索网格区域\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Uh, we're working on a broadened search grid,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.95,0:20:11.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将可变因素考虑进去  但这需要时间\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}factoring in current changes, but it's gonna take time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.47,0:20:13.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧  我一小时内过去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All right. I'm gonna be there within the hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.26,0:20:15.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望你们到时候能给出更好的回答\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm gonna want better answers than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.44,0:20:42.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,彼得·麦克利什与我情同手足\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Peter MacLeish was a brother to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.80,0:20:46.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你杀了我的亲人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You kill my family...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.00,0:20:50.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也杀你的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I kill yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.02,0:21:13.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杰森\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Jason...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.61,0:21:32.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.73,0:21:35.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道由于今晨《纽约标准》发表的文章\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know that there has been a great deal of speculation
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.03,0:21:36.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,外界流言四起\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}with regards to an article
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.20,0:21:39.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家均有诸多猜测\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that was published in this morning's New York Standard.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.13,0:21:41.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我无法证实或反驳该说法\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Although I cannot confirm or deny the allegations,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.92,0:21:44.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我可以很自信地告诉各位\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I can tell you in confidence
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.41,0:21:48.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美国政府正在进行深入调查\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that my government is in the middle of an extensive investigation
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.12,0:21:49.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而调查需要高度保密\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that is highly classified.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.31,0:21:51.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很遗憾  此时此刻\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Unfortunately at this time,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.23,0:21:52.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由于涉及到国家安全\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I cannot share that information with you
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.84,0:21:55.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我无法向大家透露更多信息\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}because of reasons of national security.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.11,0:21:58.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总统先生  我们一定会继续支持你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mr. President, you can be assured of our continued support.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.36,0:21:59.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你  总理\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you, Chancellor.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.66,0:22:01.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本着互相理解的精神\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Then, in the spirit of mutual understanding,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.76,0:22:03.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我建议我们回到\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I suggest that we move over
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.07,0:22:05.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,裁剪核军备的提案上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to the initiative regarding nuclear disarmament.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.54,0:22:07.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  总统先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm sorry, Mr. President.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.65,0:22:10.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但法方不同意\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But France is not satisfied.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.39,0:22:13.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想提醒一下新任的美国总统\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}May I remind the new American president
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.90,0:22:16.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当你下令要在阿尔及利亚\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that when he initiated a mission
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.42,0:22:19.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抓捕马吉德·纳萨尔时\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to capture Majid Nassar in Algeria,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.24,0:22:22.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们给予了美军使用法国领空的许可\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}we allowed him to use French airspace.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.26,0:22:25.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们还利用了西班牙的雷达装备\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Spanish radar assets and Italian naval support
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.18,0:22:27.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以及意大利的海军资源\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}were also employed.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.29,0:22:30.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而现在我们必须要面对的事实是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now, we must all face the fact that we supported you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.42,0:22:33.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美方可能有意欺骗我们提供军事支持\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}under what might turn into c.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.73,0:22:35.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们有权知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We deserve to know
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.19,0:22:39.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾尔萨卡是否真的并非国会爆炸案的真凶\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}if Al-Sakar did not perpetrate the Capitol bombing.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.18,0:22:42.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怕我国政府也持相同意见  总统先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm afraid my government agrees, Mr. President.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.26,0:22:44.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们已经从伊拉克吸取到了教训\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We have learned from our mistakes in Iraq.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.32,0:22:45.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在未得知事情真相前\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We cannot discuss your initiative any further
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.95,0:22:47.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们无法进一步讨论您的提案\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}without knowing the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.12,0:22:49.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请容我说几句\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If my esteemed colleagues will excuse me,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.85,0:22:52.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位不会真觉得\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}you are not seriously suggesting
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.03,0:22:55.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,法国及英国手上没有因涉及国家安全\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that the French and British don't have classified intelligence
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.95,0:22:59.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而必须进行保密的情报吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that they keep secret for reasons of national security.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.31,0:23:00.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mais oui.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.79,0:23:04.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们当然也有  摩斯国务卿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Of course we have our discretions, Secretary Moss.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.19,0:23:08.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我们也有理由互相信任\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But we also have reason to trust each other,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.47,0:23:12.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟我们有长期合作的经验\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}a long history of cooperation and experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.36,0:23:15.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而我们和柯克曼先生没有共事过\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Monsieur Kirkman has no such history.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.58,0:23:18.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他能当上总统\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He is president only because
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.08,0:23:21.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是因为前政府被消灭了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the previous government was wiped out.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.78,0:23:25.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  我的意思是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, my point is...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.88,0:23:30.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们要如何去相信一个...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}how can we trust someone who appears to be a --
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.77,0:23:31.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪个词来着\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What's the word?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.49,0:23:34.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愚蠢的  笨拙的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Gaffeur. Maladroit.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.82,0:23:38.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想你是想说"糊涂虫"\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I believe the word you're searching for is "Blunderer."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.90,0:23:40.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oui.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.46,0:23:46.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你让我们协助你去追捕一个错误的目标\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Who apparently abused article five of the NATO charter
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.45,0:23:51.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这显然违反了《北约宪章》第五条\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}by asking us to assist him in going after the wrong target.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.20,0:23:54.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正如我之前所说  夫人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}As I said earlier, Madame,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.03,0:23:57.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不方便对我已发表的言论\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I am not at liberty to comment on that any further
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.14,0:23:58.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做出深入的评价\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}than I already have.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.92,0:24:02.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那法国方面建议\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Then France proposes tabling any discussion
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.10,0:24:03.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搁置对美方提案的一切讨论\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}of the U.S. Initiative
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.65,0:24:07.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直到总统先生能给出更多的表态\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}until the president can say more and does.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.68,0:24:12.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能做的...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All I can do...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.66,0:24:17.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有请求大家\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}is ask you all, please...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.21,0:24:22.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请不要让我国国内的问题\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}please do not allow my nation's domestic issues
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.08,0:24:24.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,影响到我们的全球目标\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to interfere with our global objectives.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.00,0:24:26.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我提请核计划集团\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Then I move to have the Nuclear Planning Group
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.86,0:24:29.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今日午后再次讨论这项提案\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}revisit the initiative this afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.57,0:24:30.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,核计划集团\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The Nuclear Planning Group
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.84,0:24:34.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将在上午的会议后  重新考虑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}will meet after the morning session to...reconsider.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.18,0:24:35.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.96,0:24:38.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在我们来讨论一些日程上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now let's move to some of the less...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.10,0:24:41.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,争议没那么大的项目吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}controversial items on our agenda.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.06,0:24:48.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,追踪器已经安装好了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The trace has been planted.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.90,0:24:51.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果有人想删这些电子文件\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If someone deletes these digital files,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.53,0:24:53.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们就能追踪到那混蛋了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}we'll be able to track the bastard.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.23,0:24:57.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别留到后面一起感谢我啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Don't thank me all at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.23,0:25:03.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  好了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All right, all right. Way to go, Abe!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.03,0:25:04.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢  非常感谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you. Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.81,0:25:07.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢  回去工作吧  够了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you. Go back to work. Enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.86,0:25:09.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  谢谢各位\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All right, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.64,0:25:12.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  感谢各位\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All right. Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.68,0:25:13.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-太棒了  做得好  -谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Good job. Great job. - Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.85,0:25:14.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没收到我的短信吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You didn't get my texts?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.99,0:25:17.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在忙着让我们成名\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, I've been busy making us famous.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.46,0:25:18.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,进来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.12,0:25:21.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,埃布·莱纳德  这是艾丽莎·阿布德\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Abe Leonard, Alyssa Abboud.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.02,0:25:25.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是要讨论晋升机会吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Uh, are we here to discuss promotional opportunities?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.34,0:25:27.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事实上  艾丽莎是来提供法律意见的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Actually, Alyssa's from Legal.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.68,0:25:30.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,联调局想跟你谈话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The FBI wants to talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.59,0:25:36.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是意料之中啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's so predictable.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.68,0:25:38.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是没想到这么快\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I just didn't expect it this soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.72,0:25:39.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,埃布\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Abe --
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.46,0:25:41.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好几周了  他们都不肯听我的电话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}For weeks, I couldn't get them on the phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.01,0:25:43.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们甚至派人跟踪我想吓跑我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They even put a tail on me to try and scare me off.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.11,0:25:44.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么  现在他们倒想跟我谈话了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What? Now they want to talk?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.94,0:25:47.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得了吧  我不会跟他们谈的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I mean, forget it. I'm not talking to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.06,0:25:48.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们希望你去谈\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We'd like you to.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.82,0:25:49.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  你说什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm sorry. What?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.82,0:25:51.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们认为你可能是国会爆炸案调查中的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They believe that you could be a potential witness
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.41,0:25:53.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,潜在目击者\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}in their investigation into the Capitol bombing.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.50,0:25:55.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能  我不会供出我的消息来源的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No way. I'm not giving up my sources!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.99,0:25:57.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有人要你这么做\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No one's asking you to.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.99,0:25:59.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你们要我做什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So what are you asking me?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.04,0:26:01.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就参加一个简单的问询  仅此而已\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}To go in for an interview. That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.14,0:26:02.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-看看他们想要什么  -凭什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- See what they want. - Why should I?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.80,0:26:04.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为如果你拒绝  他们可以传唤你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Because they can subpoena you if you don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.51,0:26:05.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行啊  让他们尽管来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Fine. Let 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.81,0:26:08.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾丽莎的意思是  如果你自愿去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What Alyssa's saying is if you go in voluntarily,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.15,0:26:10.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对你和杂志社都有好处\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}it buys good will, for you and the paper --
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.52,0:26:12.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟社里给你提供了时间  金钱和支持\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the paper that gave you the time and money
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.16,0:26:13.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让你拿到了这个报道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and support to get this story.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.46,0:26:16.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许还能因他们的麻烦再赢个普利策奖呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, and possibly pick up another Pulitzer for their troubles.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.15,0:26:20.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我请求你  埃布\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm asking you, Abe.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.27,0:26:23.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,社里希望你去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is what New York wants.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.17,0:26:25.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这对我很重要\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's important to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.31,0:26:36.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.07,0:26:39.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就这么定了吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, I guess it's a date.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.32,0:26:41.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们一小时后从这里出发\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We'll leave together from here. One hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.68,0:26:47.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她有什么不满啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What's her problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.00,0:26:49.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她代表新闻记者方出席\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She represents journalists.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.83,0:26:55.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还没跟我说空军一号的事呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You never told me about Air Force One.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.90,0:26:58.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不敢相信你居然选在今天问我这种事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I can't believe you're asking me about that on a day like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.70,0:26:59.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想知道情况怎么样啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I want to know how it went.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.98,0:27:01.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在都要忙疯了  艾米丽\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm really crazy-busy right now, Emily.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.76,0:27:03.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每个人现在都忙疯了  赛斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Everyone is crazy-busy right now, Seth.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.91,0:27:05.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就快点告诉我吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Really quickly, just tell me,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.15,0:27:07.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切都如你所愿吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}was it everything you'd hoped it'd be?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.33,0:27:09.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么说吧  我的预期\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let's just say that the anticipation
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.17,0:27:11.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被现实打败了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}far outweighed the actual event.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.55,0:27:12.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是这么听说的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So I heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.51,0:27:17.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你什么意思  摩斯告诉你了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What do you mean? Moss told you?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.73,0:27:20.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他好像给我发了张照片\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He may have sent me a photo.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.35,0:27:23.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们友尽了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We are no longer friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.66,0:27:30.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}美国海岸警卫队
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.58,0:27:34.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,费尔南德兹  我是法索探员\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Fernandez? Agent Foerstel.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.45,0:27:36.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-很高兴见到你  -请汇报最新情况\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Nice to meet you. - Status update.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.15,0:27:37.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的搜索面积覆盖了这一整片区域\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We've covered this entire area.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.53,0:27:38.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目前没有消息\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So far, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.46,0:27:40.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不能接受\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's unacceptable.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.32,0:27:42.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那艘船肯定关掉了应答器\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The ship must have disabled its transponder.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.49,0:27:43.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再加上海浪汹涌及飞机的飞行下限\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You add in rough seas and a low ceiling,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.98,0:27:45.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更使我们的搜索难度加倍了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}it makes the search twice as difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.82,0:27:48.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我需要你动用手头的一切资源\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I need you to put every resource you have on this.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.21,0:27:49.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经在做了  先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's already being done, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.59,0:27:51.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但以我的经验来看\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But, in my experience,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.54,0:27:53.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要找到一艘不愿被发现的船是很难的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}it's hard to find a ship that doesn't want to be found.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.77,0:27:55.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不管  找到它\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't care. Find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.67,0:28:05.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请进\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.86,0:28:08.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我们为下午的会议起草的文稿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's the readout we drafted for the afternoon session --
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.13,0:28:09.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除去了美方提案的部分\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}minus the U.S. Initiative.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.76,0:28:11.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是些标准套路\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's just standard boilerplate.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.09,0:28:13.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果您没意见的话  我就发给记者团\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If you're good with it, I'll get it out to the pool.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.30,0:28:16.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没问题  发吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is fine. Send it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.09,0:28:18.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-谢谢  -赛斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Thank you. - Seth...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.16,0:28:23.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感谢你今天下午所做的一切\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you for what you did this afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.14,0:28:25.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您是说在世界舞台上垂死挣扎吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You mean dying on the world stage?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.58,0:28:27.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.43,0:28:30.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟透了对吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Pretty awful, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.85,0:28:32.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就直说了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, look, I'll be honest.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.17,0:28:34.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那只是我做的又一个绘声绘色的简报\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It was one of my more colorful briefings.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.99,0:28:38.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但您的工作比我的要艰巨多了  尤其是现在\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But your job is way harder than mine, especially right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.79,0:28:40.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感谢你能这么说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I appreciate you saying that.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.75,0:28:43.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也很感激你没有要求更多消息\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I appreciate you not asking for more information.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.52,0:28:45.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我认识您有一段时间了  总统先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, I've known you for a while now, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.19,0:28:47.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,足以让我知道  当您做出一个决定时\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Long enough to know that, uh, when you make a decision,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.65,0:28:50.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定是有充分理由的  这对我来说就够了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}it's for a good reason, and that's good enough for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.27,0:28:52.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是希望媒体也能够满意\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just wish it was good enough for the press.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.59,0:28:53.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.22,0:28:55.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  这可能是重要消息\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Excuse me. This might be important.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.90,0:28:57.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赛斯·怀特\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Seth Wright.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.11,0:29:00.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.97,0:29:04.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,核计划小组表决了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The Nuclear Planning Group voted.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.57,0:29:07.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们不会将您的提案重新提上议程\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They're not gonna be putting your initiative back on the agenda.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.93,0:29:09.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那也没办法了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So that's it then.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.06,0:29:14.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总统先生  第一夫人打电话找您\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sir, the First Lady's on the phone for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.20,0:29:15.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.86,0:29:17.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很遗憾  总统先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm sorry, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.75,0:29:18.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次再来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.06,0:29:28.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾丽克斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Alex.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.55,0:29:30.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切都还好吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Everything all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.95,0:29:33.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们没事  你呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're fine. How are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.18,0:29:36.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不太好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've been better.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.14,0:29:39.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很遗憾\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.03,0:29:40.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道这一定很不容易\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know this can't be easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.55,0:29:43.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.57,0:29:51.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我整天都在想你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So, I've -- I've been thinking about you all day.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.25,0:29:53.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道的  那个新闻\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You know, the story.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.93,0:29:56.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得我理解了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I-I think I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.65,0:29:58.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理解什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Understand what?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.44,0:30:01.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在医院里不肯告诉我发生了什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You shutting me out at the hospital
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.56,0:30:04.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当那个联邦调查局探员去见你的时候\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}when that FBI agent came to see you...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.47,0:30:08.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每次麦克走进来时你的反应\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the way you react every time Mike enters a room...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.24,0:30:11.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有你不让我们的家庭\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the reason you can't let the family
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.42,0:30:13.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回白宫住的原因\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}come back to the White House.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.17,0:30:15.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是真的  是吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's true, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.95,0:30:17.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,炸毁国会大厦的另有其人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Someone else blew up the Capitol,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.37,0:30:19.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你并不知道是谁  对吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and you don't know who it is, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.26,0:30:22.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,汤姆\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tom?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.19,0:30:25.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有太多事情我一直都想告诉你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There are so many things I've wanted to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.38,0:30:28.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在仍想告诉你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So many things I still want to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.41,0:30:29.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是你不能\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But you can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.77,0:30:34.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在想\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I was thinking,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.80,0:30:35.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一年前\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}a year ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.64,0:30:39.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在工作日唯一需要担心的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the only thing I ever had to worry about on a weekday
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.72,0:30:42.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是我能否按时去看佩妮的足球训练\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}was whether or not I'd get to Penny's soccer practice on time.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.96,0:30:45.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这像是上辈子的事了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That is a lifetime ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.39,0:30:47.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.07,0:30:53.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,汤姆  我能怎么帮你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tom, how can I help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.39,0:30:58.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别对我失去信心\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Don't lose faith in me.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.79,0:31:00.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.43,0:31:04.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是永远支持你的  不是吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm always on your side, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.49,0:31:11.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吗  知道了  谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay? Got it. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.47,0:31:13.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们应该找到他们了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I think we found 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.37,0:31:14.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在哪儿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.56,0:31:15.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巴尔的摩港口\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Port of Baltimore.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.97,0:31:17.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们刚刚接到了一艘未经安排出航的货轮\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They just received a call from an unscheduled freighter
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.81,0:31:19.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发出的呼叫  要求卸货  位置已锁定\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}looking to unload cargo. Location works out.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.90,0:31:21.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概什么时候抵达\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When it's estimated to arrive?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.19,0:31:23.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不到一小时  216号船位\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Less than an hour. Slip 216.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.00,0:31:24.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是法索\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes. Foerstel.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.54,0:31:26.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我需要一个人质拯救小组\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I need an HRT en route to
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.41,0:31:28.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去巴尔的摩港口216号船位\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the Port of Baltimore, Slip 216.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.00,0:31:29.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会去那儿和他们汇合\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm gonna meet them there.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.45,0:31:34.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莱纳德先生  谢谢你过来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mr. Leonard, thank you for coming in.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.34,0:31:36.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我的荣幸\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My pleasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.68,0:31:37.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们可以开始了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Should we get started?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.86,0:31:40.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我必须回答这个问题吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do I have to answer that?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.09,0:31:46.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不同意\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You don't agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.61,0:31:47.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可没这么说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's not what I'm saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.91,0:31:49.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你觉得这成不了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But you don't think it'll work.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.45,0:31:50.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的想法现在并不重要\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What I think doesn't matter right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.90,0:31:52.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是总统的想法\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's what the president thinks.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.05,0:31:54.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而我支持总统\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I support the president.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.02,0:31:57.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马塞特首相\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now, Prime Minister Massett
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.25,0:31:59.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同意给你五分钟时间\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}has agreed to give you five minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.41,0:32:00.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.66,0:32:04.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好利用起来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Make 'em count.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.97,0:32:07.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,五分钟后见\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}See you in five minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.29,0:32:10.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.92,0:32:13.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你来见我  夫人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you, Madame, for seeing me.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.14,0:32:19.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你理解我们为什么将提案移出了议程吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You understand why we took the initiative off of the agenda.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.44,0:32:23.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不赞成  但是是的  我理解\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I did not agree with it, but, yes, I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.05,0:32:25.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我需要赢得你的信任\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I need to earn your trust.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.34,0:32:28.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不只是我  还有所有北约成员国\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, not just me. All of NATO.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.42,0:32:30.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.62,0:32:32.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我想从法方开始\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But I would like to start with France.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.86,0:32:35.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个削减武器之梦是我们一起开启的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We began this dream of weapons reduction together.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.72,0:32:37.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也需要你来完成这个梦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I will need you there to finish it.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.49,0:32:40.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你打算怎么做呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And how do you expect to do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.43,0:32:42.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会向你证明美方\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}By proving to you that the United States is serious
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.94,0:32:45.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在削减核威胁上是认真的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}about reducing the nuclear threat.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.79,0:32:48.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我国拥有200枚导弹\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My country has 200 missiles
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.35,0:32:50.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,散布在欧洲各地的地堡中\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}in bunkers scattered across Europe.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.67,0:32:52.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,俄罗斯的数量是我们的两倍\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Russia has twice that number.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.49,0:32:54.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老式的确保相互摧毁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The old dogmas of mutually assured destruction
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.75,0:32:56.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对阵二次打击能力的教条\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}versus secondary strike capabilities
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.95,0:32:59.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,需要严肃地重新审核\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}need to be seriously re-examined,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.48,0:33:00.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尤其考虑到我们的控制系统\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}especially given the threat
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.51,0:33:02.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有被黑入的风险\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}of our control systems being hacked.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.07,0:33:03.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可是个骇人的想法\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's a terrifying thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.66,0:33:04.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes, it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.98,0:33:06.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,外面部署的武器越多\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And the more weapons that are out there,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.50,0:33:08.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出现闪失的可能性就越大\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the greater chance something could go wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.30,0:33:10.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对我来说很简单\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}For me, it is very simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.53,0:33:14.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们想给后代留下怎样的世界\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What kind of a world do we want to leave our children?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.81,0:33:23.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是个梦想家  总统先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You are a dreamer, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.44,0:33:24.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.83,0:33:25.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错  我是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes, I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.84,0:33:28.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会为此道歉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I won't apologize for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.37,0:33:32.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经让摩斯国务卿开始\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I have asked Secretary Moss to begin
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.06,0:33:34.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与俄罗斯进行双边会谈了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}bilateral negotiations with Russia
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.69,0:33:36.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望你能尽快加入我们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}in the hopes that you will join us soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.59,0:33:39.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夫人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Madame...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.38,0:33:42.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真心希望你能加入我们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I do hope you join us.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.84,0:33:45.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我相信无论法方去哪  北约都会追随\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Because I believe wherever France goes, NATO will follow.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.49,0:33:53.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我希望我们能在下次峰会更详细地讨论这个问题\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I hope we can discuss this more fully at the next summit.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.95,0:34:00.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也希望如此\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I would like nothing more.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.81,0:34:14.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}白宫安全网络许可
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.99,0:34:26.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}标记文件被删除
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.19,0:34:33.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里特\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ritter.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.99,0:34:35.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们找到那个混蛋了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We got the son of a bitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.15,0:34:37.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他在哪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.92,0:34:41.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,西翼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The West Wing.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.15,0:34:57.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  目标在移动  直走右转\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay, our guy's on the move. Go straight and take a right.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.72,0:35:00.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错  继续走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah. Keep going.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.93,0:35:01.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有多远\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How much farther?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.82,0:35:03.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走廊尽头左转\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Take a left at the end of the hallway.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.79,0:35:07.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等  等等  右转\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Wait, wait, wait, wait, wait. Actually take a right.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.44,0:35:12.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  等等\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No. Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.38,0:35:13.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我到底要去哪  恰克\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where am I going, Chuck?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.55,0:35:15.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  不  不  别啊  别\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, no, no, no. Come on. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.92,0:35:16.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.26,0:35:23.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们要找的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Our guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.49,0:35:28.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克隆了自己的电子足迹\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He cloned his digital fingerprint.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.56,0:35:30.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}临界状态\N系统崩溃
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.89,0:36:00.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可怜的孩子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Poor guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.65,0:36:02.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可不是他预期的旅行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not quite the trip he expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.54,0:36:04.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁都没想到这趟会是这样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not quite the trip anyone expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.38,0:36:06.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,的确\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}True enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.94,0:36:07.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.12,0:36:09.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What for?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.19,0:36:10.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,支持我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}For standing by me.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.74,0:36:11.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个嘛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.03,0:36:13.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也没给我多少选择\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}you didn't give me much choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.01,0:36:16.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要是栽了  我得和你一起栽\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If you go down, I go down with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.04,0:36:17.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是认真的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm being serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.16,0:36:18.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, I am, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.40,0:36:21.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你都要把我逼疯了  汤姆\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You know, you drive me nuts, Tom.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.89,0:36:24.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有时候真是太...学术了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're just so damn... academic at times,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.34,0:36:26.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都想给你的头来一巴掌\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I want to slap you upside the head.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.09,0:36:31.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我要是没看出你身上的特质  我就太糟了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But damn if I don't see something special in you,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.39,0:36:33.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,某种特质\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}something that might --
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.84,0:36:36.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甚至可能让你接近伟人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}well, might even approach greatness...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.64,0:36:40.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要你不马失前蹄\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}...if you don't trip over your own feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.27,0:36:43.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢  我想该这么说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you. I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.27,0:36:48.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我们还留得青山在  不怕没柴烧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But we're not out of the woods yet. Not by a long shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.07,0:36:50.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可能暂时挽回了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You may have salvaged some credibility
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.61,0:36:52.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,北约的一些信任\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}with NATO for the time being,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.04,0:36:54.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但稍后降落时会有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but we're gonna have a whole new firestorm
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.97,0:36:56.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全新的暴风烈火等着我们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}waiting for us when we land.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.66,0:36:57.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.96,0:37:00.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,准备好了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You ready for it?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.18,0:37:03.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必须不准备好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm gonna have to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.13,0:37:13.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,柯克曼总统将于今日下午返回\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}President Kirkman returns this afternoon
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.97,0:37:16.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而政局却与他昨天离开时\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to a very different political landscape
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.00,0:37:18.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大相径庭\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}than the one he left just yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.23,0:37:24.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}柯克曼面临艾尔萨卡事件难题
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.77,0:37:20.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,埃布·莱纳德的爆炸性声明\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Abe Leonard's bombshell story,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.04,0:37:22.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,指出艾尔萨卡不是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}which asserts Al-Sakar was not responsible
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.56,0:37:24.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,袭击国会大厦的罪魁祸首\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}for the attack at the Capitol,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.29,0:37:26.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一举震动了华盛顿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}sent shock waves through Washington,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.23,0:37:28.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对总统来说这时机不能更差了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and it couldn't have come at a worse time for the president,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.75,0:37:31.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他正好在第一次国际访问途中\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}who's at the height of his first international trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.68,0:37:33.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很多人称之为柯克曼不长的总统生涯中\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Many are calling this the worst day
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.69,0:37:35.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最糟的一天\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}of Kirkman's young presidency.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.71,0:37:53.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快走  快\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let's go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.92,0:37:56.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-快点  -向我六点钟方向前进\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Let's go! - Move up on my six.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.28,0:37:58.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-走  -跟上  走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Let's go. - Follow 'em up. Go, go, go.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.63,0:38:00.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Go. Go, go.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.84,0:38:01.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.81,0:38:05.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-不许动  -联调局  举起手来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Freeze! - FBI! See those hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.62,0:38:07.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.00,0:38:09.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-没有人  -没有人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Nothing. - Nothing, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.57,0:38:16.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,警惕\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Eyes open.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.32,0:38:18.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,联调局  举起手来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}FBI! Put your hands up!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.08,0:38:18.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-不许动  快点  -举起手来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Don't move! Do it now! Now! - Hands up!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.82,0:38:20.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趴下  趴下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Get down! Down!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.93,0:38:26.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-走  -带他下楼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Let's go. - Take him downstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.55,0:38:28.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安全了  长官\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're all clear, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.69,0:38:31.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打开所有的集装箱进行搜索\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I want every container opened and searched.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.05,0:38:32.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,威尔士在船上的某处  找到她\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Wells is somewhere on board. Find her.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.71,0:38:33.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-是  长官  -走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Yes, sir. - Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.56,0:38:35.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把他们带下来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let's get them down there now.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.17,0:38:37.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趴在地上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}On the ground!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.98,0:38:54.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个没人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This one's clear!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.88,0:39:00.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All clear!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.46,0:39:04.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全都没人  长官\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All clear, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.40,0:39:06.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-检查别的  -这个呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Let's check the others. - What about this one?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.68,0:39:09.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个被焊封起来了  长官\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's welded shut, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.89,0:39:11.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就炸开\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, blow it.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.60,0:39:19.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,设置好了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, we're set here.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.46,0:39:31.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.69,0:39:35.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,准备好了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're all set here.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.49,0:39:40.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,启动炸药  要爆炸了  找掩护\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let's go! Fire in the hole! Cover!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.21,0:39:45.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-走  -门开了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Go. - Door's open.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.03,0:40:09.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}约翰·埃德加·胡佛联调局大楼\N车库二层
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.26,0:40:12.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趴在地上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}On the ground right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.70,0:40:13.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手放在脑后\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Get your hands behind your head!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.98,0:40:16.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-跪下  -跪下  快\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Get on your knees! -Get down! Now!
